# OD sync runtime artifacts — ALL local, none tracked (spec 206 hygiene).
# Daily --check / apply reports (*.md) are regenerable verbose logs and are NO
# LONGER committed: they leaked absolute paths into a public repo and shipped
# needlessly to consumers. The durable audit (vendor SHA + last_check timestamps
# + history) lives in vendor/open-design/MANIFEST.json. Tarball cache, extraction
# scratch, and staging dirs were never tracked.
*.md
tarball-*.tar.gz
extracted-*/
staging-*/
